Titolo: Fights in Tight Spaces

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Fights in Tight Spaces is a roguelike deck-building tactical game developed by British studio Ground Shatter and published by Mode 7 Games. The game was released in December 2021 for Microsoft Windows and Xbox One, after an Early Access period that started in February 2021. 
The game is based on simulating the melee combat of one protagonist against many enemies in close quarters common in action films, using turn-based combat with playing cards representing various moves the player can make.

Genere: Roguelike deck-building 

Valutazione: 78
